TimeString/--background--

   NAME
	TimeString -- ... (V12)

   FUNCTION
	TimeString is a Custom Class of the Magic User Interface © by Stefan
	Stuntz. It's a subclass of string-class and time-class.

	The idea of this class was born during developing my Gregor
	application.

	MUI public custom class that displaying a string gadget for time
	strings. The display format of the time string can be freely defined.
	An input string can be parsed by the given format string, or in
	various standard formates.

   NOTES
	None.

